      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified-1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.6/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/a92dfb0a-ceff-11e4-b37b-5254006e85c2).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures in this session, but a previous session failed for this commit.",
